        <abstract> 
<p>Will bring MS [of vol. 1 of <hi rend="italic">Living Cirripedia</hi>] on the last day of July, and proofs of the eight plates now engraved will be sent soon. CD has failed to get materials for the one coloured plate he wanted, so none will be in colour. There will be ten altogether. He will ask later whether he must pay for the extra one. G. B. Sowerby Jr comes next day to complete drawings for two not yet engraved.</p> 
